    "output": "Implemented Excalidraw injection/extraction plan from task 3f410b5d. Rebuilt and redeployed prod.\n\n## Changes\n- src/pages/Draw.tsx: excalidrawAPI ref, initialData load, debounced onChange auto-save (2s)\n- server/index.ts: GET/POST /api/drawings/:id, GET /api/drawings list, SSE broadcast\n\n## Bug fix\nOld server returned 200+HTML (SPA fallback) for /api/drawings/*, causing infinite loading. Fixed by restarting dev server and rebuilding prod container.\n\n## Verified via curl\n- GET /api/drawings/default returns 404 when empty, saves and loads after POST\n- Both dev (3002) and prod (3001) working\n- tsc --noEmit passes"
